<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_04_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_04_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">낚시 도구 한 세트에는 통발 2개와 미끼통 5개가 들어 있습니다. 통발의 수는 미끼통의 수의 몇 배인지 구해 봅시다.​</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <div class="img_row flex align_start">
              <div class="picture_wrap">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0002_content.png" alt="" />
                <button class="zoom"></button>
              </div>

              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">미끼통의 수에 대한 통발의 수의 비를 써 보세요.​</h3>

                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2 : 5"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_2">
            <div class="img_row flex align_start">
              <div class="picture_wrap">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0002_content.png" alt="" />
                <button class="zoom"></button>
              </div>

              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">앞의 비에서 기준량과 비교하는 양은 각각 얼마인지 써 보세요.​</h3>

                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="row">
                    <span class="f32b">기준량: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="5"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row">
                    <span class="f32b">비교하는 양: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_3">
            <div class="img_row flex align_start">
              <div class="picture_wrap">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA614_04_SU/0002_content.png" alt="" />
                <button class="zoom"></button>
              </div>

              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">통발의 수는 미끼통의 수의 몇 배인지 분수와 소수로 각각<br />나타내어 보세요.​</h3>

                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="col col1">
                    <span class="f32b">분수: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(5)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span class="f32b">배</span>
                    <span class="comma">,</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col col2">
                    <span class="f32b">소수: </span>
                    <div class="input_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="0.4"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span class="f32b">배</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
        <article class="page page_4">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize promise">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>
              <div><span lang="y">기준량에 대한 비교하는 양의 크기를</span> <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1">비율</button><span lang="y" class="small-gap">이라고 합니다.</span></div>
              <div class="summarize_ex">
                <div lang="y" class="summarize_ex_1">
                  <div>(<span class="txt1">비율</span>)=(<span class="txt2">비교하는 양</span>)&divide;(<span class="txt3">기준량</span>)=</div>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>(<span class="txt2">비교하는 양</span>)</span>
                    <span>(<span class="txt3">기준량</span>)</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div lang="y">
                <span>비 2:5를 비율로 나타내면&nbsp;</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>5</span>
                </span>
                <span>또는 0.4입니다.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
